TIMESHEET_SEND_EMAIL webhook
Received: {{now}}

Recipient
- Name: {{payload.toName}}
- Email: {{payload.toEmail}}

Context
- Date: {{payload.date}}
- Today Column: {{payload.todayColumn}}

Instruction
Use the prompt template in askalx/timesheet-prompt-template.md section 2 (Send Reminder Email).
Send a concise reminder email via gmail preset, then return strict JSON only:
{"status":"sent","to":"{{payload.toEmail}}"}
