{"status":"failed","to":"{{payload.toEmail}}","error":"reason"}
No markdown, no extra text.

XERO_SECURE_BRIDGE_QUERY webhook
Received: {{now}}

Input payload
- action: {{payload.action}}
- params: {{payload.params}}

Security requirements
- Use only this endpoint: http://127.0.0.1:8790/xero/query
- Use header Authorization: Bearer ${OPENCLAW_BRIDGE_TOKEN}
- Use Content-Type: application/json
- If OPENCLAW_BRIDGE_HMAC_SECRET is present, add:
  - x-timestamp: current unix seconds
  - x-signature: hex(HMAC_SHA256(OPENCLAW_BRIDGE_HMAC_SECRET, `${x-timestamp}.${rawBody}`))

Allowed actions only
- list_overdue_invoices
- list_unpaid_bills
- get_contact

Request body to bridge (strict)
{"action":"{{payload.action}}","params":{{payload.params}}}

Return strict JSON only:
{"ok":true,"action":"...","data":{...}}
If bridge call fails, return strict JSON:
{"ok":false,"action":"{{payload.action}}","error":"reason"}
No markdown, no extra text.
